Package: ufcscrapeR
Title: Scrape UFC and Pride Fight Data from UFCStats.com
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dave", "Yount", email = "dave@sportanalytics.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The `ufcscrapeR` package provides tools for scraping comprehensive
    UFC and Pride fight data directly from UFCStats.com. It extracts round-by-round metrics,
    total fight statistics, and detailed performance indicators (such as strikes, takedowns,
    and control time) for both fighters. The returned data is clean and structured,
    making it ideal for predictive modeling, data visualization, and advanced MMA analytics.
